Adrian was grateful that the annual dinner of the Royal Society for Medicine had been
held at the Dorchester last year.
"Where's Harvey?" bleated Stephen.
"Only forty yards behind you."
Stephen quickened his pace and ran up the steps of the Dorchester and pushed
