direction of the gallery, his hopes rising with each stride. James took the lift to the first
floor and nearly ran to Room 120. He banged on the door. Stephen jumped at the
noise. He didn't feel he could face Harvey again.
"James, it's you. Cancel the room, pay for one night and then join me in the cocktail
bar."
