"What do we do for the rest of the week?" enquired James innocently.
Stephen resumed control.
"We master the green dossier—backwards, frontwards and sideways for a full dress
rehearsal on Friday. The most important thing for you, James, is to get a grip of
yourself and let us know what you intend to do."
James sank back into gloom.
