then contact Doctor Barker and ask if he can get to the hospital immediately. Tell him
it's an emergency. This gentleman requires a surgeon of the highest qualifications."
"You're damn right I do," said Harvey as he passed out. Jean Pierre left the Casino and
called over his transmitter:
"Action stations!—action stations!"
Adrian left the Hotel de Paris and took a taxi. He would have given a hundred
