"I tell you what, let's catheterise him for a couple of days. That'll cramp his style. Look,
it must be pretty boring for you cooped up here all day. Why don't you come and have
a spot of supper with me after Mr. Metcalfe has gone to sleep tonight?"
"I should love to, docteur. Where shall I meet you?"
