file:///F|/my%20folder/my%20ebooks/Ebooks%20-3/...A%20Penny%20More,%20Not%20A%20Penny%20Less.html (184 of 199)4/17/2006 5:21:04 AMNot a Penny More, Not a Penny Less by Jeffrey Archer
James took the lift to the seventh floor and joined the others for coffee.
